,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:53:47.000Z","msg":"你個老細話上帝叫佢選特首果陣<br />\n你有冇叫佢搵上帝見你呀？"},{"pid":"6e9c90e55c58e7a9edfbb51e1d086e75ffaf3395","tid":1218268,"uid":26106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:59:54.000Z","msg":"牧師都證實左佢地無舉旗就狂放催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但個句野真係忍唔住笑左<br />\n警犬咁都講得出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7c34863d294a4b0943e76ba81a8de8bcee5f2b","tid":1218268,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:16:04.000Z","msg":"不如星期日組隊<br />\n一邊拍片<br />\n一邊問名記低<br />\n同時一隊帶望遠鏡睇清楚個no.<br />\n方便日後認人跟進<br />\n黑警無一個係無辜"},{"pid":"d5e55a9eb0c6ea2e346bc7311a465ca74b8cdba6","tid":1218268,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:19:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99b1606fff69cf05e3a0617d6ed1d682094b2b58","tid":1218268,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:40:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}